    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I recently started writing a brand new app in PHP 5.3.0 and registered my own 'namespace'.
When I reference a 'Zend_' namespaced class from within my PHP namespace the Loader does not
resolve it properly unless used like that \Zend_Cache::METHOD.</p>

<p>I have resolved the issue by extending the Zend_Loader's method and applying the fix to the loadClass method.</p>

